# AxiomApe - Cloudflare Pages _redirects
#
# NOTE: /about, /contact, /privacy 301 rules to *.html were removed.
# Cloudflare Pages already serves /about.html etc. directly AND auto-redirects
# /about.html -> /about (clean URLs). Combined with a 301 rule sending /about
# back to /about.html, this created an infinite redirect loop, which is why
# axiomape.com/about.html, /about, /contact.html, /contact, /privacy.html, and
# /privacy were all returning empty/blank pages. Removing the rules lets
# Cloudflare's built-in handling serve these pages normally.

# Catch-all: any unmatched path goes to the homepage
# (Remove this if you want GitHub-style 404 for unknown tool slugs)
